<section>
<title>Detailed Description</title>

<para>The RDRAND entropy Provider: RDP <?linebreak?>Provides access to the Intel RDRAND entropy provider. This provider is not recommended for stand-alone use, but should be combined with another entropy provider to seed a MAC or DRBG function to provide quality random output. The ACP entropy provider is the recommended provider in this library. </para>
</section>
